I've made this twice now for party guests. It was a big hit both times, although they were a little too hot the second time. This was because I let them marinade much longer (1.5 hours) as opposed to the 15 minutes the first time. It's also possible that I added too much pepper, but I'm sure it was mostly due to longer marinading time. Peeling and deveining was also time-consuming, but the results are well worth it.

